006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model;
007
008import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.datatype.markup.MarkupMultiline;
009
010import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
011import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.Nullable;
012
013/**
014 * A marker interface for Metaschema constructs that can be members of a
015 * Metaschema definition's model.
016 */
017public interface IModelElement extends IDefaultable {
018
019  /**
020   * Get the Metaschema model type of the information element.
021   *
022   * @return the type
023   */
024  @NonNull
025  ModelType getModelType();
026
027  /**
028   * Retrieves a string that uniquely identifies the model element in the overall
029   * collection of model elements. This should the type of element, it's name, and
030   * any additional information needed to uniquely identify it.
031   *
032   * @return the coordinates
033   */
034  @NonNull
035  String toCoordinates();
036
037  /**
038   * Retrieve the remarks associated with this information element, if any.
039   *
040   * @return the remarks or {@code null} if no remarks are defined
041   */
042  @Nullable
043  MarkupMultiline getRemarks();
044
045  /**
046   * Retrieves the Metaschema module that contains the information element's
047   * declaration.
048   *
049   * @return the Metaschema module
050   */
051  // REFACTOR: move to definition
052  @NonNull
053  IModule getContainingModule();
054}
